


1) Tools for Designing
Photoshop - Cutouts , textures , and small edits
Illustrator - clean ui animation used for animation (like front page etc, use simlple shapes and animate them)

2)  For clean and complete edits - one editing software and one motion design software
Adobe premium - editing, cutting, putting everything together (free software Davinci Resolve )
Adobe after effects - Motion , animation and VFX (Fusion inside Davinci resolve same purpose).


3 Level of learning

Foundation level

- Basic tutorial the boring stuff - learn the interface, tools
- make simple edits - montages, travel vlogs and reels
- cutting to beat , colour correction, types of cuts

Intermediate Level of learning

- Music based editing  - stop cutting randomly , start cutting with music, place cut on beats, use rise and fall of song, match energy of track with visuals
- Basic animations - scale , position , rotation
- Sound Design - wooshes , hit music, ambience,
- colour Grading - Fixing skin tones for people to look natural, matching different clips to make the scene look same, Simple LUTS
                  Pacing - high paced edits - quick cuts , fast visuals, constant movements.
                  Slow paced edits - you see in documentaries - longer shots , calmer pacing


once your edit start looking decent next step is how it can look different
Advanced Level of learning -  how should it look different

- Motion design inside after effects
- advanced path animations-  
- Advanced transitions

Finding your style
- watch videos edits ,shorts - catch the transitions study it






